Set up a new submodule

  $ cd
  $ git init -q -b main newsub
  $ cd newsub
  $ touch d
  $ sl commit -m 'Add d' -A d
  $ cd ../parent
  $ git submodule --quiet add -b main ../newsub
  $ sl status newsub
  ? newsub

Add a new submodule

  $ sl add newsub
  $ sl status newsub
  A newsub

Forget a submodule

  $ sl forget newsub
  $ sl status newsub
  ? newsub

